---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="季節活動" description="北海道札幌四季活動總整理，冬季雪祭、夏季花季、秋季賞楓、春季櫻花，每個時節都有不同的精彩。">
  <Header />

  <main>
    <div class="page-hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>季節活動</h1>
        <p>北海道四季皆有精彩，每個時節都值得造訪</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <!-- Spring -->
      <section class="season-section spring">
        <div class="season-header">
          <div class="season-emoji">🌸</div>
          <div class="season-title">
            <h2>春季</h2>
            <span class="season-months">3月 - 5月</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="events-grid">
          <div class="event-card">
            <div class="event-month">3月中～4月</div>
            <h3>札幌樱花季</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">北海道大學校園、大通公園、中島公園都是知名賞櫻景點。札幌的櫻花比東京晚約兩週，4月底是最佳觀賞期。</p>
            <div class="event-highlights">
              <span>🌸 札幌氣象台周邊</span>
              <span>🌸 北海道大學銀杏並木</span>
              <span>🌸 中島公園</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="event-card">
            <div class="event-month">4月下旬</div>
            <h3>千代浦公園樱花節</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">當地人推薦的賞櫻秘境，遠離觀光客人潮，悠閒享受花見時光。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Summer -->
      <section class="season-section summer">
        <div class="season-header">
          <div class="season-emoji">🌻</div>
          <div class="season-title">
            <h2>夏季</h2>
            <span class="season-months">6月 - 8月</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="events-grid">
          <div class="event-card featured">
            <div class="event-month">7月</div>
            <h3>北海道薰衣草花季</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">富良野與美瑛的薰衣草田正值花季，紫色花海如夢似幻。從札幌出發當日來回可行，建議搭乘薰衣草號觀光巴士。</p>
            <div class="event-highlights">
              <span>💜 富田農場（Kinotake）</span>
              <span>💜 拼布之路</span>
              <span>💜 紫色隧道</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="event-card">
            <div class="event-month">6月底～7月</div>
            <h3>YOSAKOI索朗祭</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">北海道最大規模的舞蹈祭典，穿著特色服裝的舞者在街上遊行，音樂與掌聲不斷，氣氛熱闘。</p>
            <div class="event-highlights">
              <span>💃 大通公園主舞台</span>
              <span>💃 免費觀賞</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="event-card">
            <div class="event-month">7-8月</div>
            <h3>札幌夏祭</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">市中心舉辦的夏季活動，有屋台小吃、傳統表演與花火大会。適合全家同樂。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-card">
            <div class="event-month">8月</div>
            <h3>札幌花火大會</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">豐平川花火大會是北海道最大規模的煙火活動之一，數千發煙火照亮夜空。</p>
            <div class="event-highlights">
              <span>🎆 豐平川岸</span>
              <span>🎆 免費觀賞</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Autumn -->
      <section class="season-section autumn">
        <div class="season-header">
          <div class="season-emoji">🍁</div>
          <div class="season-title">
            <h2>秋季</h2>
            <span class="season-months">9月 - 11月</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="events-grid">
          <div class="event-card">
            <div class="event-month">9月下旬～10月中旬</div>
            <h3>賞楓季節</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">北海道的楓葉比本州早紅一個月。山區與市區同步換裝，赤紅、金黃、橙色交織成大片地毯。</p>
            <div class="event-highlights">
              <span>🍁 藻岩山纜車賞楓</span>
              <span>🍁 定山溪溫泉</span>
              <span>🍁 大雪山國立公園</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="event-card">
            <div class="event-month">10月</div>
            <h3>札幌秋季三富祭</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">北海道最具傳統色彩的秋季祭典，在定山溪舉行，有神轎遊行與當地美食。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-card">
            <div class="event-month">9-10月</div>
            <h3>食材的季節</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">秋季是北海道食材最豐富的時期。秋刀魚、松茸、蘋果、南瓜、葡萄相繼上市，是美食愛好者的最佳旅遊時機。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Winter -->
      <section class="season-section winter">
        <div class="season-header">
          <div class="season-emoji">❄️</div>
          <div class="season-title">
            <h2>冬季</h2>
            <span class="season-months">12月 - 2月</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="events-grid">
          <div class="event-card featured">
            <div class="event-month">2月</div>
            <h3>札幌雪祭</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">世界知名的冬季盛典，始於1950年，毎年吸引超過200萬旅客。大通會場展出巨型雪雕，冰雕作品晶瑩剔透，夜晚點燈後如夢似幻。</p>
            <div class="event-highlights">
              <span>🏔️ 大通會場：巨型雪雕</span>
              <span>🏔️ 薄野會場：冰雕展示</span>
              <span>🏔️ TSUDOMU會場：冰雪滑梯</span>
            </div>
            <div class="event-note">
              <strong>📅 2026年日程：</strong>2月初至中旬（確切日期每年公告）
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="event-card">
            <div class="event-month">12月底～</div>
            <h3>聖誕市集</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">大通公園周邊搭建聖誕木屋，贩卖德式聖誕小吃與手工藝品，營造濃厚的聖誕氛圍。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-card">
            <div class="event-month">12月～2月</div>
            <h3>札幌白色燈飾</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">市區主要街道與公園有白色燈飾布置，札幌站周邊與大通公園的燈飾最具人氣。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-card">
            <div class="event-month">11月下旬～</div>
            <h3>滑雪季開始</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">札幌周邊有多座滑雪場，著名的有手稻滑雪場（可遠眺市區夜景）與札幌藻岩山滑雪場。約11月底開始營業。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-card">
            <div class="event-month">2月</div>
            <h3>定山溪雪物語</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">定山溪溫泉區的冬季活動，有雪燈走廊、雪地活動，泡湯之餘還能賞雪景。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-card">
            <div class="event-month">1月</div>
            <h3>札幌冰雪公主遊行</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">雪祭期間的熱闘活動，穿著婚禮服的「冰雪公主」在市中心遊行。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Monthly Calendar -->
      <section class="guide-section alt-bg">
        <h2 class="section-title">📅 月份活動一覽</h2>
        <div class="calendar-table">
          <div class="calendar-row header">
            <span>月份</span>
            <span>活動</span>
            <span>推薦程度</span>
          </div>
          <div class="calendar-row"><span>1月</span><span>滑雪季、札幌雪祭準備</span><span>⭐⭐⭐⭐</span></div>
          <div class="calendar-row"><span>2月</span><span>札幌雪祭（最大盛典）</span><span>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</span></div>
          <div class="calendar-row"><span>3月</span><span>初春、賞雪最後時機</span><span>⭐⭐⭐</span></div>
          <div class="calendar-row"><span>4月</span><span>賞櫻（晚於本州）</span><span>⭐⭐⭐⭐</span></div>
          <div class="calendar-row"><span>5月</span><span>新綠、觀光淡季</span><span>⭐⭐⭐</span></div>
          <div class="calendar-row"><span>6月</span><span>薰衣草季節前、YOSAKOI</span><span>⭐⭐⭐⭐</span></div>
          <div class="calendar-row"><span>7月</span><span>薰衣草旺季、花季</span><span>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</span></div>
          <div class="calendar-row"><span>8月</span><span>花火大会、夏祭</span><span>⭐⭐⭐⭐</span></div>
          <div class="calendar-row"><span>9月</span><span>初秋、美食季節</span><span>⭐⭐⭐⭐</span></div>
          <div class="calendar-row"><span>10月</span><span>賞楓（早於本州）</span><span>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</span></div>
          <div class="calendar-row"><span>11月</span><span>賞楓尾聲、滑雪準備</span><span>⭐⭐⭐</span></div>
          <div class="calendar-row"><span>12月</span><span>聖誕市集、白色燈飾</span><span>⭐⭐⭐⭐</span></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Tips -->
      <section class="guide-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">💡 旅遊建議</h2>
        <div class="tips-cards">
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>❄️ 冬季</h3>
            <p>雪祭期間住宿價格高且容易客滿，建議提前2-3個月預訂。穿著防滑鞋，注意電車與公車可能延誤。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>🌻 夏季</h3>
            <p>富良野花季是北海道最旺季，務必提早預訂交通與住宿。早起出發可以避開人潮與塞車。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>🍁 秋冬季</h3>
            <p>賞楓時節短暫，建議關注紅葉情報網站。滑雪則要注意各雪場的開放時間。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>🌸 春季</h3>
            <p>賞櫻人潮比東京少，悠閒度取勝。4月底可同時賞櫻與補雪（山區）。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary) 0%, #2d2d4a 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .hero-content p {
    opacity: 0.85;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
  }

  main {
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Season Sections */
  .season-section {
    padding: 3.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .season-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .season-emoji {
    font-size: 3rem;
  }

  .season-title h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .season-months {
    color: #888;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .season-section.spring .season-header { border-bottom: 3px solid #FFB7C5; }
  .season-section.summer .season-header { border-bottom: 3px solid #F5A623; }
  .season-section.autumn .season-header { border-bottom: 3px solid #D2691E; }
  .season-section.winter .season-header { border-bottom: 3px solid #87CEEB; }

  .spring .season-header { border-color: #FFB7C5; }
  .summer .season-header { border-color: #F5A623; }
  .autumn .season-header { border-color: #D2691E; }
  .winter .season-header { border-color: #87CEEB; }

  .events-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .event-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .event-card.featured {
    grid-column: span 2;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #fff5f5 100%);
    border: 2px solid var(--primary);
  }

  .event-month {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .event-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .event-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .event-highlights {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .event-highlights span {
    background: #f5f5f5;
    color: #555;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }

  .event-note {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    background: #fff3e0;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #555;
  }

  .event-note strong {
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  /* Calendar */
  .guide-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .alt-bg {
    background-color: #f0ede8;
    margin: 0 -1.5rem;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .calendar-table {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .calendar-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .calendar-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .calendar-row.header {
    background: var(--secondary);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .calendar-row:nth-child(even):not(.header) {
    background-color: #fafafa;
  }

  .calendar-row span:first-child {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    width: 80px;
  }

  .calendar-row span:nth-child(2) {
    flex: 1;
    color: #555;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .calendar-row span:last-child {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  /* Tips */
  .tips-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .tip-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .tip-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .tip-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .events-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .event-card.featured {
      grid-column: span 1;
    }

    .tips-cards {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .tips-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .calendar-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.25rem;
    }

    .alt-bg {
      margin: 0;
      border-radius: 0;
    }
  }
</style>